<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sweet Hot Sizzlers - Cafe Menu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f1ea;
            color: #5c3d2e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #6d4c41;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #8b5e3b;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #5c3d2e;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5c3d2e;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6d4c41;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        Sweet Hot Sizzlers - Cafe Menu
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">
        <h2>Delicious Sweet Hot Sizzlers</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Chocolate Lava Sizzler <span class="price">₹250</span></h3>
            <p>Warm chocolate cake with a molten center, topped with vanilla ice cream and drizzled with chocolate syrup.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Apple Cinnamon Sizzler <span class="price">₹230</span></h3>
            <p>Spiced apples with cinnamon, nutmeg, and brown sugar, served sizzling with vanilla ice cream.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Banoffee Sizzler <span class="price">₹260</span></h3>
            <p>Caramelized bananas and toffee sauce over a buttery biscuit base, topped with ice cream and caramel drizzle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Sizzling Brownie with Ice Cream <span class="price">₹280</span></h3>
            <p>Fudgy brownie served sizzling with vanilla or chocolate ice cream.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Sizzling Strawberry Sundae <span class="price">₹240</span></h3>
            <p>Fresh strawberries with whipped cream, chocolate, or caramel syrup on a sizzling plate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Sizzling Pineapple with Honey and Nuts <span class="price">₹220</span></h3>
            <p>Caramelized pineapple cooked in honey, cinnamon, and nuts, served with ice cream.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Sizzling Churros with Chocolate Sauce <span class="price">₹270</span></h3>
            <p>Hot, crispy churros served sizzling with rich chocolate sauce.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Sizzling Apple Pie <span class="price">₹250</span></h3>
            <p>Classic apple pie filling on a hot plate, topped with ice cream and caramel drizzle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Sizzling Mango Delight <span class="price">₹230</span></h3>
            <p>Sweet mangoes sautéed with cinnamon and honey, served sizzling with ice cream.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Sizzling Chocolate Banana Fudge <span class="price">₹260</span></h3>
            <p>Warm bananas cooked in chocolate sauce and fudge, served sizzling with vanilla ice cream.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
